album.name: Black Mass for a Mass Grave

wiki.summary: The eighth full-length album by Inquisition. A music video was made for the track "Luciferian Rays". Recorded at Orbit Audio Studios in Seattle, Washington from August 3rd to August 8th, 2020. Mixed & mastered from August 19th to September 5th, 2020 at Boom! Studios in Berkeley. Line-up: Dagon - Vocals, guitars, keyboards Incubus - drums Above Chaos - cover art Alejandro Corredor - Producer, recording, mixing, mastering Read more on Last.fm.
